    </content>
    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>SERI News, January 17</title>
      <lead>Information from the State Secretariat for Education, Research and Innovation SERI: Switzerland’s ERI policy for 2017–2020 / swissnexday’16 / Project contributions 2017–2020 / ...</lead>
      <text link="no">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New four-year period in the promotion of education, research and innovation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Switzerland’s ERI policy for 2017–2020 explained in nine points&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Long-term care&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Measures against labour market shortages in nursing care&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key features of draft Cooperation in Education Act (CEdA)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Confederation and the cantons lay foundations for cooperation in education&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education policy focus on vocational qualifications for adults&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Two studies explore the needs of companies and adult learners&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Higher Education Act (HEdA)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Entry into effect of implementing provisions on coordination and funding of Swiss higher education sector&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project contributions 2017–2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;15 broad-based projects promote cooperation between universities&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;swissnexDay‘ 2016 on 15 December in Basel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Meetings, presentations and discussions on ‘The Future of Ageing’&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EUR 10 billion towards the further development of European aerospace&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;ESA Ministerial Council meeting in Switzerland a success&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</text>
      <contact>info@sbfi.admin.ch</contact>
